These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram, roller, van
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, musical, superhero, family
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Transport          | van | roller | tram | quad-bike   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | spy     | superhero   | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, peach, cucumber, tomato
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, zinnia, daisy, azalea
1. the person eating tomato is the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
3. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
4. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | cucumber | tomato | peach | pumpkin    |
| Flower   | daisy    | zinnia      | orchid | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, black, chestnut, amber
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, almond-milk, coffee
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person who likes pink is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Color         | pink | amber | chestnut   | black |
| Beverage   | cola   | almond-milk | coffee | milk         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, card-games, woodworking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, zinnia, begonia, daisy
1. the person who growszinnia is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | woodworking | fishing | gardening  | card-games      |
| Flower         | zinnia | daisy   | begonia | dahlia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, project-manager, pilot, electrician
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily, tulip, daffodil
1. the project-manager is on the left of the videographer##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the right of the pilot##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Job   | electrician | pilot | project-manager | videographer |
| Flower    | azalea       | daffodil | tulip | lily     |

