.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, blue, white, emerald
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, mystery, epic
1. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes white##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who likes white##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Color   | emerald | white | orange | blue |
| Movie-Genre           | animation      | mystery | epic | scientific    |

