.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
City: edinburgh, prague, hamburg, berlin
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, milk, cola
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| City   | hamburg | prague | edinburgh | berlin  |
| Beverage           | milk | almond-milk | cola       | mirinda |

