.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, fishing, woodworking
City: marseilles, san-francisco, hamburg, new-york
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby         | fishing | hiking      | card-games | woodworking |
| City   | marseilles          | san-francisco | hamburg     | new-york    |

