.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, australian, indian, polish
4 different pets are kept: hamster, pony, bird, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the french is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the polish is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | australian    | indian       | french | polish   |
| Pet     | pony | bird | rabbit   | hamster |

