.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, swisher, old-henry, prince
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, american, mexican, italian
1. the indonesian is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the italian is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the american is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Cigar    | aristoff | old-henry  | swisher | prince |
| Nationality   | italian | mexican | american          | indonesian    |

