.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
City: paris, boston, edinburgh, san-francisco
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, blueberry, potato, orange
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating potato##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to boston is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| City      | edinburgh | boston  | paris | san-francisco |
| Food   | zucchini  | potato | orange           | blueberry   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, ebony, red, purple
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, kiwi, kale, blueberry
1. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
2. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
4. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
5. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Color   | ebony | pink | purple | red  |
| Food           | blueberry | kiwi      | kale | pomegranate |

