.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
House: cottage, cape-cod, ranch-style, palace
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, black, azure, amber
1. the person who likes amber is the cottage house##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the cottage house##1
3. the ranch-style house is the person who likes azure##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who likes black##1
5. the palace house is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| House   | ranch-style | cape-cod  | cottage | palace   |
| Color        | azure | black | amber    | blue |

