2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

