.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, chestnut, azure, green
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, february, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who likes green##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Color   | azure | green     | coral | chestnut |
| Birthday         | december | november | october   | february   |

