.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-16::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, helicopter, quad-bike, tram
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, begonia, daffodil, marigold
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Transport           | skateboard | tram    | helicopter    | quad-bike |
| Flower   | begonia      | daffodil | tulip | marigold       |

