.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, havana, davidoff, oliveros
House: cape-cod, tower, modern, craftsman
1. the craftsman house is the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is the tower house##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the modern house##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the craftsman house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar   | havana      | davidoff | oliveros | cain |
| House     | cape-cod | craftsman    | modern  | tower |

