.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, salsa, disco, classical
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bongani, swisher, alhambra
1. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre      | indie   | classical | salsa   | disco      |
| Cigar   | vegafina | alhambra      | bongani | swisher |

