.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, badminton, weightlifting, baseball
4 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, snooker, backgammon
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing snooker is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Sport         | badminton | weightlifting | baseball | volleyball |
| Game   | backgammon     | snooker    | poker      | mah-jongg   |

