.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, davidoff, ritmeester
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, rock, soul, pop
1. the fan of blues is on the left of the game-smoker##1
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of blues is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | davidoff | game | ritmeester   |
| Music-Genre     | soul  | blues    | rock       | pop |

 